Package: python-mechanicalsoup
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: Automated interaction with websites
 mechanicalsoup is a Python library for automating interaction with
 websites. MechanicalSoup automatically stores and sends cookies,
 follows redirects, and can follow links and submit forms. It does
 not do Javascript.
 .
 This package contains the mechanicalsoup Python module.
